    <text>
        <body>
            
            
            <div xml:id="Short8"> 
                <interpGrp type="poembox">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="free"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="sad"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="society"></interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <lg> 
                    <l>From blocks away the music floats</l>
                    <l>to my enchanted ears.</l>
                    <l>It build. It's here! And then it fades-</l>
                    <l>and I explode in tears.</l>
                    <l></l>
                    <l>I kick the TV set, and scream,</l>
                    <l>sobbing to extort her,</l>
                    <l>while Mom stares at One Life to Live,</l>
                    <l>and won't give me a quarter.</l>
                    <l></l>
                    <l>I pause, change tactics, snatch a coin</l>
                    <l>from the bottom of her purse,</l>
                    <l>then race to catch the ice-cream truck,</l>
                    <l>ignoring Mama's curse.</l>
                    <l></l>
                    <l>I stop the truck, I start to choose - </l>
                    <l>then see I won't be eating.</l>
                    <l>I stare down at a goddamn dime,</l>
                    <l>and trudge home to my beating.</l>
                    
                    
                    
